channel.title: Gang Wars MMORPG
channel.description: hey there everyone. I am korn and a few of my friends and i are in the very early process of making a mmorpg. The story line is going to be made up of 3 rival gangs fighting for territory. I as just wondering what kind of stuff you people would like to see in a mmorpg. If any of you might be interested in working for me and helping out you will need to know how to use GameSpace, and you have to be fun to work with. I need imput though, like what weapons i should put in, and missions and quests, and other stuff like that. Help me out people. Thanks, Korn P.S to all you teenagers out there i am looking for your imput over most people.
